Subject: [PATCH 4/4] fix(eval): make seam receipts replay on current checkout

Refresh the generated seam receipts after moving witness artifacts to plugin paths and make QIT fixture refs project-relative so content addresses do not depend on the checkout root.

Constraint: Fresh-main verification applies the series in a throwaway worktree under /private/tmp

Rejected: Keep absolute fixture paths in QIT provider refs | makes committed receipt hashes checkout-root dependent

Confidence: medium

Scope-risk: narrow

Tested: LEV_UPDATE_QIT_BRIDGE_RECEIPT=1 pnpm --dir core/eval exec vitest run src/cr-qit-bridge-stream-v0.test.ts

Tested: LEV_UPDATE_WORLD_ENGINE_SEAM_RECEIPT=1 pnpm --dir core/eval exec vitest run src/world-engine-seam-receipt.test.ts

Not-tested: CI
